cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL

The paper proposes a framework for cost-sensitive classification using deep neural networks, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and computational linguistics (cs.CL). However, since the paper focuses on visual data sets, cs.CV is the most likely category, followed by cs.LG and cs.AI.
